author: Warhammer
description:
Rust is getting cosmetics inspired by the Death Korps of Krieg, bringing their grim, war-forged resolve to the island.

This pack delivers battle-scarred wargear, inspired by one of Warhammer 40,000’s most fearless regiments.

Gear up and march across the island clad in their signature equipment:
Death Korps of Krieg hazmat suit – Reskin of the hazmat suit with the classic Krieg gas mask and trench coat look.

Death Korps of Krieg backpack – Rugged field pack for the survivalist soldier.

Death Korps of Krieg chainsword – Fire up the chainsword - a brutal chainsaw reskin. 

Death Korps of Krieg shotgun – A grimdark firearm with real stopping power.

Death Korps of Krieg storage containers – Two Krieg-styled storage barrels.

Wishlist Now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3891560/Rust_Warhammer_Pack/
